Package: builder
Title: 'R' Package Preprocessor with Macro Support
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
        person(given = "John",
               family = "Coene",
               role = c("aut", "cre"),
               email = "jcoenep@gmail.com"),
        person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane",
               family = "Toure",
               role = "ctb",
               email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com")
    )
Description: Bundles and builds the 'builder' preprocessor binary from vendored
    'C' sources. 'builder' expands macros, directives, conditionals, and more in
    'R' source files. Provides 'R' wrapper functions around the compiled binary
    for use as a build-time tool in other 'R' packages.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
SystemRequirements: GNU make, C compiler, R development headers and
    libraries (libR, libpcre2, libzstd, liblzma, libbz2, libz)
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    utils
Suggests:
    tinytest
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/devOpifex/builder
BugReports: https://github.com/devOpifex/builder/issues
